  "final_text": "I'll run `stm32 debug start` \u2014 the ELF will be autodiscovered from the project descriptor if present.\nThe project descriptor identifies an **STM32N6** device, which requires the BOOT switch to be in **dev mode** before the debug session can start.\n\n**Action required:**\n1. Physically set the **BOOT switch** on your board to **dev mode** (BOOT0 = 1 / dev-mode position \u2014 consult your board's silkscreen or schematic).\n2. Once the switch is set, I'll re-invoke with `--n6-dev-mode` to confirm and start the session.\n\nReady to proceed when the BOOT switch is in dev mode?"
}